This module does not load any PETSc installation. You should set PETSC_DIR, PETSC_ARCH and LD_LIBRARY_PATH to a local installation. 
For example:
export PETSC_DIR=your-petsc-dir
export PETSC_ARCH=arch-linux-c-opt
export LD_LIBRARY_PATH="$LD_LIBRARY_PATH:$PETSC_DIR/$PETSC_ARCH/lib"


To install the library, run pip install . in the folder where you downloaded the encapsulatedpgd repo


